      "stem_html": "<p>Identify the reagents <b>a</b>–<b>f</b> in the following scheme:</p>\n<img class=\"scaled-down\" src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBZ1FXIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--cbaa0d216c7bf6e8f6d741cfd26dc3654b8bcd5d/OChem_17_EC_052.jpg\" alt=\"Cyclohexanol reacts with reagent a to form cyclohexanol. b to form cyclohexylbromide. c to form cyclohexylmethanol. d to form cyclohexanecarbaldehyde, e to form 1-cyclohexyl-2-phenylethanol, f to form (E)-(2-cyclohexylvinyl)benzene.\">",
